          <div class="feature-strip-item"><span class="feature-num">02</span><div><h4>Built to Last</h4><p>Premium 304-grade stainless steel frame, engineered for enduring quality and total corrosion resistance.</p></div></div>
          <div class="feature-strip-item"><span class="feature-num">03</span><div><h4>Superior Clarity</h4><p>4mm ecological silver glass - crafted without copper or lead for unparalleled optical brilliance.</p></div></div>
          <div class="feature-strip-item"><span class="feature-num">04</span><div><h4>Flexible Installation</h4><p>Two sizes, two orientations. Bathroom-ready. Fits every space, every vision.</p></div></div>
