          <div class="feature-strip-item"><span class="feature-num">01</span><div><h4>Industrial Elegance</h4><p>A bold Matte Black finish that anchors any interior - from the minimal to the eclectic.</p></div></div>
          <div class="feature-strip-item"><span class="feature-num">02</span><div><h4>Built to Last</h4><p>Premium 304-grade stainless steel frame engineered for enduring quality and total corrosion resistance.</p></div></div>
          <div class="feature-strip-item"><span class="feature-num">03</span><div><h4>Superior Clarity</h4><p>4mm ecological silver glass - crafted without copper or lead for unparalleled optical brilliance.</p></div></div>
          <div class="feature-strip-item"><span class="feature-num">04</span><div><h4>Flexible Installation</h4><p>Two sizes, two orientations. Bathroom-ready. Fits every space, every vision.</p></div></div>
        {% elsif tl2 contains 'solenne' %}
          <div class="feature-strip-item"><span class="feature-num">01</span><div><h4>Sculptural Presence</h4><p>An oversized organic silhouette that goes beyond function - a genuine work of art for your interior.</p></div></div>
          <div class="feature-strip-item"><span class="feature-num">02</span><div><h4>Small-Batch Craft</h4><p>Each Solenne is hand-crafted in small batches, ensuring individual attention and uncompromising quality.</p></div></div>
          <div class="feature-strip-item"><span class="feature-num">03</span><div><h4>Pristine Clarity</h4><p>5mm ecological glass - thicker, heavier, and visually perfect. Copper-free, lead-free production.</p></div></div>
          <div class="feature-strip-item"><span class="feature-num">04</span><div><h4>Two Ways to Display</h4><p>Lean it for effortless elegance or wall-mount it with included hardware. Both positions are extraordinary.</p></div></div>
        {% elsif tl2 contains 'rib' %}
